column5: As the ice season is right around the corner, thought I'd share some footage of Big Walleye from Nippising in a fully decked out icehut. The ice hut was equipped with 8 beds, a kitchen and heated bathroom. https://youtu.be/cKoJEGt-sw0
Nice fish, thanks for the share. Have a great icefishing season!

Thanks. Let's hope for a long cold winter. One where the lakes aren't over run with bait fish and the fish are cooperative where I can sit back and not be in tournament concentration mode for a bite. Haha. Sent from my iPhone using Tapatalk
